<item chapterid="603039" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1939" articlename="女秘书日记" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521787131" lastupdate="1521787131" chaptername="第697章没有半点的隐私" chapterorder="696" size="6508" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    “那康明是什么时候给你写下那封保证书的？”唐鸣问道，手里拿出那封保证书。

