<item chapterid="603048" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1939" articlename="女秘书日记" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521787131" lastupdate="1521787131" chaptername="第706章实事求是" chapterorder="705" size="6313" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    车子停在古南省的省委党校门口，大门口也一样弄了一块石头，仿照中央党校的样子，在上面刻了四个字：实事求是。

