<item chapterid="603166" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1939" articlename="女秘书日记" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521787131" lastupdate="1521787131" chaptername="第824章爱不释手" chapterorder="823" size="6319" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    这两位美女官员因为家住省城，所以不在党校住宿，每天都回家去住。

