<item chapterid="603563" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1939" articlename="女秘书日记" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521787131" lastupdate="1521787131" chaptername="第1220章飞起了红晕" chapterorder="1220" size="6646" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    “好，我相信，汪总的战略战术，每次都是很成功的！”张贤发说道。

