<item chapterid="604325" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1939" articlename="女秘书日记" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521787131" lastupdate="1521787131" chaptername="第1979章美到了骨髓里" chapterorder="1982" size="6648" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    下午五点半，于涛果然准时来到了陆大妮居住的小区接她。

